# GitHub only requires ONE matching approval, not all of them.
/libs/    @Ticket-Souq/infra-team @Ticket-Souq/eureka-team @Ticket-Souq/auth-team @Ticket-Souq/ticket-team @Ticket-Souq/venue-team @Ticket-Souq/analytics-audit-team @Ticket-Souq/notification-team @Ticket-Souq/availability-locking-team @Ticket-Souq/event-team @Ticket-Souq/payment-team @Ticket-Souq/reservation-team

/infra/   @Ticket-Souq/infra-team

